{
  "stem": "1033.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And we were counted out and we were counted in.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And about-- the end of February, early March, I was sick.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I was put into what they call a [INAUDIBLE] camp.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And it was another place where we were living in huts covered with earth.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And there, because of my experience, I was put into the kitchen, but for a very short time because my friend [INAUDIBLE] was there from the village [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And I stole potatoes for him in the-- I tied my pants and I put them in where my trousers were.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "And I got caught and I lost my job.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "And I understand that he had survived and he's in Israel somewhere.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "His name is [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "And he would remember this story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "Anyhow, as the time grew on, they put us on-- one day, they put us on trains.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "[INAUDIBLE] thinks we're relaxed.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "This was April, mid- April.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And we were on the road for a long time-- maybe 10 days.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "I remember a military train stood next to us and it got machine-gunned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And as we were walking, I saw a hand-- just nothing, only a hand in the snow.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "You know, through that fog of being numb, it still-- it felt bizarre.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And then we got into a place we didn't know where it was at night.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And in the morning, the Americans walked in.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I am there waving to them.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "And my picture was, to my amazement, in the paper five years ago.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
